{"tid":1275762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「長遠方案」P牌終有一日甩P","createTime":"2019-07-01T22:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T23:00:56.000Z","uid":76916,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8c8609eb204624e64d158311bbbfab94e7766a","tid":1275762,"uid":76916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:49:00.000Z","msg":"相信大家都睇到無數咁多P牌新AC開post帶風<br />\n唔排除一部分係真心想參與一份先開AC<br />\n但其他立心不良嘅新AC終會甩P<br />\n咁只會令成個討論區敵我難分<br />\n到時只會淪為第二個舊登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想大家趁今日唔洗上前線嘅幫連子諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想借機會多謝死士義士，前線記者，文宣<br />\n始終我有顧慮唔敢衝上前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過今次我見大家真係做到兄弟爬山<br />\n我就知大家都為左自己嘅家去all in！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人 加油</span>"},{"pid":"60abea8e0ddd6f1e2328147e6e489c1af466cc7c","tid":1275762,"uid":76916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:00:56.000Z","msg":"負評嘅出黎講下問題係邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}